# Technical Specification: CarpoolConnect

## System Architecture Diagram
```mermaid
graph TD
    subgraph Client_Layer
        A[Mobile App - iOS/Android]
        B[Web Dashboard - Admin/Sustainability]
    end

    subgraph API_Gateway_Layer
        C[API Gateway / Load Balancer]
    end

    subgraph Service_Layer
        D[Auth Service - SSO/OIDC]
        E[Matching Engine - Geo-Spatial]
        F[Commute Service - Trip Lifecycle]
        G[Analytics Service - ESG/Metrics]
    end

    subgraph Data_Layer
        H[(User DB - PostgreSQL)]
        I[(Ride DB - MongoDB)]
        J[(Geo-Cache - Redis)]
    end

    subgraph External_Integrations
        K[Azure AD / Okta]
        L[Google Maps API]
    end

    A & B --> C
    C --> D & E & F & G
    D --> K
    E --> L
    E --> J
    F --> I
    G --> H & I